{"tid":1133014,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"投票者4701人總票數超過一萬張，日本網友票選「由大家決定最佳100首平成動畫歌」","createTime":"2019-04-30T17:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T09:21:57.000Z","uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c6a92adb4dfa36741bb4fe1d9d1cd495ea4f46af","tid":1133014,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/85522/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F85522%2F&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=af9f7b3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/85522/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/00-95.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F00-95.jpg%3F&h=c3c71f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong>投票者4701人總票數超過一萬張，日本網友票選「由大家決定最佳100首平成動畫歌」<br />\n</strong>作者: 填海紳士 日期: 30/04/2019<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Only_my_railgun.jpg?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FOnly_my_railgun.jpg%3F&h=850fa967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟之前由索尼大法旗下日本索尼音樂娛樂舉辦，由業界評審選出的「平成Anisong大賞」不同<br />\n<br />\n這個【由大家決定最佳100首平成動畫歌】結果是由日本網友投票得出的<br />\n<br />\n投票者人數4701人，總票數超過一萬張，在這榜單內不乏大家熟悉的動畫歌<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hkacger.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/00.png?\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F00.png%3F&h=4e987258&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而在這個以平成為範圍的投票中，能獲得眾多日本網友青睞脫穎而出的TOP3歌曲就是：<br />\n<br />\n第3位306票，《科學超電磁砲》OP「only my railgun」<br />\n<br />\n第2位392票，《化物語》ED「君の知らない物語」<br />\n<br />\n第1位413票，《涼宮春日的憂鬱》IN「God knows&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n100〜91位<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1119931814301188097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1119931814301188097&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=441f2ff6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1119931814301188097&h=d46ac6c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1119931814301188097</a><br />\n<br />\n90〜81位<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1120289698478313472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1120289698478313472&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=5f912467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1120289698478313472&h=5b29ed81\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1120289698478313472</a><br />\n<br />\n80〜71位<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1120654199136509952\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1120654199136509952&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=14727248\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1120654199136509952&h=e6cf5f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1120654199136509952</a><br />\n<br />\n70〜61位<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1121017289342480385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1121017289342480385&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=f5e8c2f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1121017289342480385&h=b0d2c554\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/i/status/1121017289342480385</a><br />\n<br />\n60〜51位<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/i/status/1121371296946774017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1121371296946774017&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEBmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=730a2488\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fstatus%2F1121371296946774017&h=c23d68ac\" target=\"_blank\"